TI  -  Impact of Vitamin D Supplementation on Cardiometabolic Status and Androgen Profile in Polycystic Ovary Syndrome
JA  -  https://clinicaltrials.gov/show/NCT04117750
PY  -  2019
C3  -  CTgov NCT04117750
