AB  -  INTERVENTION: Control group:Control group took esazolam tablet 1 mg every night to improve night sleep, 3 weeks as a course of treatment, 3 weekends to observe the effect ;Treatment group:Patients in the treatment group were treated with acupuncture. Tongdu TiaoShen method was used for acupuncture therapy. The main points were Baihui(GV20), Shenting(GV24), Shuigou(GV26), Dazhi(GV14) and Shendao(GV11). Liver fire disturbs the heart add Xingjian(LR2), Xia Xi(GB43); Phlegm‐heat internal disturbance plus Fenglong(ST40), Neiting(ST44); Heart and spleen deficiency plus Xinshu(BL15), Pishu(BL20); Heart and kidney imbalance add Xinshu(BL15), Shenshu(BL23); Heart‐gallbladder qi deficiency add Xinshu(BL15), Danshu(BL19); incoordination between spleen and stomach Gongsun(SP4), Zusanli(ST36). Keep the needle for 40 minutes after the above points are acupunctured, and perform the needle once at 20 minutes. One hour after the start of dialysis, acupuncture treatment was performed 3 times a week, 3 weeks as a course of treatment, and the therapeutic effect was observed over 3 weeks. ; CONDITION: Insomnia PRIMARY OUTCOME: Pittsburgh Sleep Quality IndexI scale;?‐ aminobutyric acid;cortisol;Interleukin‐1; SECONDARY OUTCOME: Kidney Disease Quality of Life Short FormF scale;triglyceride;serum albumin;Serum phosphorus;Serum Calcium;Total cholesterol;Hemoglobin;Serum parathyroid hormone; INCLUSION CRITERIA: ? The underlying disease was chronic nephritis and chronic kidney disease stage 5. Intra‐arterial venous fistula was treated with MHD, continuous dialysis with high‐efficiency dialyzer ?8 hours per week, continuous dialysis time ?3 months; ? Age =18 years and < 80 years. ? There are different degrees of sleep disorders; ? The patient has clear consciousness, voluntary participation, and good cooperation.
